Second Department,

October, 1955.

(October 3, 1955.) Cooper Lumber Company, Respondent, v. Michael Masone et al., Copartners Doing Business as Masone Brothers, Appellants.

Present — Nolan, P. J., MacCrate, Beldoek, Murphy and Ughetta, JJ. Motion for reargument denied, without costs. Present — Wenzel, Acting P. J., MacCrate, Schmidt, Beldoek and Ughetta, JJ. [See ante, p. 879.]
